{"type": "email", "id": "email_004", "subject": "Quarterly Budget Allocation Review", "from": "jessica.liu@leesmarket.com", "from_name": "Jessica Liu", "to": ["sophie.tran@leesmarket.com"], "cc": [], "date": "2023-02-25 16:30:00", "body": "Hey Sophie,

